PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774645561
OL,3,CWoman taken away from mother in forced
OL,4,Cadoption says an apology only goes so
OL,5,Cfar
OL,7,FA woman who was taken from her mother
OL,8,Fat just six weeks old says an apology
OL,9,Ffrom the government to victims of
OL,10,Fforced adoption is not enough.
OL,12,FPamela Shipley, from Nottinghamshire
OL,13,Fwas taken from her birth mother in the
OL,14,F1960's, after her mother fell pregnant
OL,15,Fafter having an affair with a married
OL,16,Fman, she was told.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774645561
OL,3,CWoman taken away from mother in forced
OL,4,Cadoption says an apology only goes so
OL,5,Cfar
OL,7,FHer mother was then sent away to a
OL,8,Fnursing home in Hertfordshire to have
OL,9,Fthe baby in secret and Pamela was put
OL,10,Finto care at just three weeks old,
OL,11,Fbefore later being officially adopted
OL,12,Fby her foster parents.
OL,14,FPamela added: "I was a shame on the
OL,15,Ffamily and there was no help with the
OL,16,Ffinances and financial support from
OL,17,Fthe government.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774645561
OL,3,CWoman taken away from mother in forced
OL,4,Cadoption says an apology only goes so
OL,5,Cfar
OL,7,F"I don't think she would of had any
OL,8,Fcounselling or support to get over the
OL,9,Ftrauma and it must of been a trauma to
OL,10,Fbe taken away from a child.
OL,12,F"I think it was pressure from social
OL,13,Facceptance which meant my mum couldn't
OL,14,Fkeep me."
OL,16,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said:
OL,17,F"The case for saying we're sorry, an
OL,18,Fappropriate apology, is very strong to
OL,19,Fmy mind. And I've already instructed
OL,20,Fthe teams to get on with this now and
OL,21,Fget to the right place."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774645561
OL,3,CWoman taken away from mother in forced
OL,4,Cadoption says an apology only goes so
OL,5,Cfar
OL,7,FIt comes as a new report from the
OL,8,FEducation Committee on Friday
OL,9,Frecommends that the government should
OL,10,Fissue a formal unqualified apology to
OL,11,Fsurvivors who have "suffered for too
OL,12,Flong".
OL,14,FThe report suggests that ministers
OL,15,Fshould begin working with survivor
OL,16,Fgroups as quickly as possible and
OL,17,Fcommit publicly to a clear timetable
OL,18,Ffor developing and issuing this.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774645561
OL,3,CWoman taken away from mother in forced
OL,4,Cadoption says an apology only goes so
OL,5,Cfar
OL,7,FHelen Hayes MP, Chair of the Education
OL,8,FCommittee said: "The state was not the
OL,9,Fonly part of the problem, there were
OL,10,Fissues within families, attitudes
OL,11,Fwithin families, the practices of
OL,12,Fvoluntary and religious organisations
OL,13,Fat the time but the government had a
OL,14,Frole to play in sustaining, supporting
OL,15,Fand perpetuating a system that did
OL,16,Fdeep damage."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774645561
OL,3,CWoman taken away from mother in forced
OL,4,Cadoption says an apology only goes so
OL,5,Cfar
OL,7,FIn post-war Britain an estimated
OL,8,F250,000 unmarried women were sent to
OL,9,Finstitutions run by religious
OL,10,Forganisations and the state, where
OL,11,Fthey were pressured and coerced to put
OL,12,Ftheir babies up for adoption between
OL,13,Fthe 1940s and 1980s. Other infants
OL,14,Fdied through poor care.
OL,16,FA report by the UK Government's Joint
OL,17,FCommittee on Human Rights (JCHR) in
OL,18,F2022 recommended ministers apologise
OL,19,Fto unmarried women who were
OL,20,F"railroaded" into unwanted adoptions.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774645561
OL,3,CWoman taken away from mother in forced
OL,4,Cadoption says an apology only goes so
OL,5,Cfar
OL,7,FPamela thinks that practical support
OL,8,Fis what's needed to help support
OL,9,Fpeople, "An apology is great, what
OL,10,Fthey need to is support for the people
OL,11,Fwho didn't have good adoptions, to
OL,12,Fgive them trauma support and
OL,13,Fcounselling.
OL,15,F"Assistance to help families and
OL,16,Ffacilitate reunions so people can
OL,17,Ffinish off their story is also really
OL,18,Fimportant."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774645561
OL,3,CWoman taken away from mother in forced
OL,4,Cadoption says an apology only goes so
OL,5,Cfar
OL,7,FKathryn Jones from Kettering, who is
OL,8,Falso a victim of forced adoption and
OL,9,Fpart of the adult adoptee movement
OL,10,Fsays, "to be frank an apology is the
OL,11,Fleast we deserve and it needs to be
OL,12,Fseen as the starting point.
OL,14,FShe added that it's "vitally important
OL,15,Fthat it's tailored because adopted
OL,16,Fmothers and birth mothers have had
OL,17,Fvery different experiences."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
